    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Once starting to soften, increase the heat to high add your <strong>diced chicken thigh</strong> and cook for 5-6 min further until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
