            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated carrot </strong>to a large bowl with <strong>half </strong>your<strong> white wine vinegar</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, give everything a good mix up and set aside – this is your<strong> carrot slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1656240604773-x200.jpg",
