      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>tahini</strong>, <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!), <strong>remaining white wine vinegar</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> cold water</strong> and a pinch<strong> </strong>of <strong>salt</strong> to a small bowl and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>tahini mayo</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
