    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fluff the <strong>fruity</strong> <strong>couscous</strong> with a fork</p><p>Top half of each <strong>warmed tortilla</strong> with the <strong>fruity couscous</strong>, <strong>spiced chicken</strong> <strong>filling</strong>, <strong>salad </strong>and <strong>carrot slaw</strong></p><p>Dollop the <strong>tahini mayo</strong> over the top</p><p>Tip: Go light on the filling on your first one so that you don't overfill the burritos!</p>",
