    {
      "instruction": "<p>To make the perfect burrito, fold the sides of each<strong> loaded tortilla</strong> in and wrap the bottom of the tortilla over the filling, tucking it in tightly</p><p>Roll the tortilla until you’re left with a burrito, then wrap them in <strong>tin</strong> <strong>foil </strong>to hold everything together – these are your <strong>Moroccan-style burritos</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>Moroccan-style burritos </strong>alongside the <strong>remaining salad</strong> and <strong>carrot slaw </strong>and enjoy!</p>",
